{"tid":1751153,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"置富一號候選人羅霄涉嫌入去投票站叫人投佢一票","createTime":"2019-11-24T16:16:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T16:31:30.000Z","uid":220066,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7e7b24ccd37b323a71fa669f829e50f8e089cabb","tid":1751153,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:16:43.000Z","msg":"話說今早去左置富投票<br />\n當入到去票站果陣<br />\n見到有位巴打發曬火話要投訢一號候選人<br />\n我問前面d人發生咩事<br />\n佢地話我聽一號候選人同其他成員入左嚟監察選民<br />\n究竟係咪投票比佢，同埋佢用眼神方式叫選民投佢一票<br />\n<br />\n我心諗乜可以咁做架咩<br />\n咁多年從來無乜候選人會入票站叫人投佢一票<br />\n其實咁樣已經觸犯舉舞弊，完全唔岩規舉<br />\n至少有幾個選民已經寫信去投訴羅霄<br />\n<br />\n羅霄呢個做法已經干擾選舉，應該可以拉得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">希望大家可以廣傳出去</span></span>"},{"pid":"5fa782922480fb3c8c5028aa1d10888485944073","tid":1751153,"uid":7741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:18:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog2_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"791e4199667d672ba435f145990e1cb1a30e54b5","tid":1751153,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:19:54.000Z","msg":"假如有足夠證據證明政府選舉造馬，香港人要立即要求宣布選舉無效，重新再選！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1751107\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1751107</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6bfd6c80d1dfb5853f053c6020a47c2a2c0aa96e","tid":1751153,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fa782922480fb3c8c5028aa1d10888485944073","tid":1751153,"uid":7741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:18:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog2_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:25:46.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"a9f450ffc2635a8b0be693e7e8ce44e1e8a06600","tid":1751153,"uid":7741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bfd6c80d1dfb5853f053c6020a47c2a2c0aa96e","tid":1751153,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike"